Documentation may be accessed directly in inc/goodput_intro.h

To generate the doxygen documentation for this package,
- run "doxygen doxyconfig" in this directory
- open docs/html/index.html with a browser.

To compile the tools, run "make all" in this directory.

To create startup scripts for the tools:
- run "create_start_scripts.sh" in the goodput/scripts directory.

To create performance measurement scripts for the tools:
- run "create_perf_scripts.sh" in the goodput/scripts directory.

